---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Free Estate Planning Tools | Mesa Estate Planning"
  description="Free interactive tools to help you understand your estate planning needs — checklists, quizzes, and calculators from Mesa Estate Planning."
  keywords="estate planning tools, estate plan checklist, trust vs will quiz, arizona estate planning"
>
  <section class="services-index-hero">
    <div class="services-index-hero-content">
      <div class="hero-eyebrow" style="opacity:1;animation:none;">Resources</div>
      <h1 class="hero-h1" style="opacity:1;animation:none;">Free tools to help you <em>get started</em></h1>
      <p class="hero-body" style="opacity:1;animation:none;">Interactive checklists, quizzes, and guides designed to help you understand what you need — before you ever talk to an attorney.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="services-index-grid">
    <div class="services-index-section">
      <div class="services-index-label">Coming Soon</div>
      <div class="services-card-grid">
        <div class="services-index-card" style="opacity:0.65;">
          <span style="font-size:0.65rem;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--bronze);font-weight:600;">Coming Soon</span>
          <h3>Estate Plan Checklist</h3>
          <p>Answer a few questions about your family and assets to find out which documents you need and why.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="services-index-card" style="opacity:0.65;">
          <span style="font-size:0.65rem;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--bronze);font-weight:600;">Coming Soon</span>
          <h3>Trust vs. Will Quiz</h3>
          <p>A quick two-minute quiz to help you understand whether a revocable living trust or a simple will is the right fit for your situation.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="services-index-cta">
      <h2>Can't wait for the tools?</h2>
      <p>The fastest way to find out exactly what you need is a free 30-minute consultation. We'll walk you through everything — no obligation.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-bronze">Book Free Consultation</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
